{
  "stem": "7157.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You know how kids are when they're five or six.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And this is when he got a little angry and slapped me on the tush.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And that's the only time he ever laid a hand on me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So he was-- I have nothing but fantastic, fond memories of my father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, the Hungarians--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Hungarians were just occupied temporarily, and everyone knew that the Germans were coming.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, we tried even before they came or right at that time to go into Russia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But unfortunately, the Russians were only interested in males of military age.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In fact, a couple of cousins of mine who survived the war were like 10 years older than me, which would mean at least 16, let's say.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were allowed to go into Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they didn't want any families and certainly no children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were kind of stuck there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Hungarians were merely, in this point, in a holding pattern, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Germans hadn't come yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I have no idea how long this lasted, whether this was a week, or three days, or two weeks, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it was a very short period of time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then the Germans came in to Stanislawow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And just to digress a little bit-- or not digress but I think I mentioned earlier that my grandparents, Ira and Golde Glotzer, were in a different little town outside of Stanislawow.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Well, the Germans came into that town already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the Germans in many ways were accompanied by Ukrainians in that part of the world.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The Ukrainians kind of jumped on the German side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And especially when it came to Jews, they were very, very anti-Jewish, to put it bluntly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And anyway, they took my grandfather away like in the first few days.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
